title: Windows 10 Pro X64 Redstone 3 MULTi-22 MARCH 2018 {Gen2}
description:
* Windows 10 Pro X64 Redstone 3 MULTi-22 MARCH 2018
* Version 1709 Build 16299.334 


[ RELEASE INFO ]


* This release contains one ISO [SOURCE ISO] and 21 executable svf-files.
* All exe-files are created from original MSDN releases.

* This is done with SmartVersion, a program that calculates the
* difference between two files (one of which is used as the source)
* and then creates an svf-file based on that difference.

* Hashes & all sources attached in separate .txt

[ DOWNLOAD INFO ]

* Download the Source ISO and preferred language
* If you want en-US then just download the SOURCE ISO.

* Run the exe-file in the same folder as the SOURCE ISO.
* This will extract the ORIGINAL ISO in the selected language.

[ CONTENTS ]

Integrated / Pre-installed:

* Servicing Stack Update:
* KB4090914
* Flash Player Security Update:
* KB4088785
* Cumulative Update:
* KB4089848

SetupComplete / Post-install:

* .NET Framework 3.5

[ EDITIONS INCLUDED ]

* Windows 10 Enterprise 2016 LTSB - STD
* Windows 10 Enterprise 2016 LTSB - KMS

* STD = Standard installation - For those with own License Key
* KMS = Activated by KMS (Exclusions are pre-set in Defender)

[ LANGUAGES ]

* ARABIC
* BRAZILIAN

* DUTCH
* ENGLISH (GB)
* ENGLISH (US)
* FINNISH

* UKRANIAN

[ SCREENSHOTS ]

[url]https://extraimage.net/image/nyO8[/url]

[ FEATURES ]

* UEFI-ready
* install.wim splitted for UEFI support (FAT32) 
* (Use attached Rufus USB-tool to make UEFI-bootable)
* Diagnostics and Recovery Toolset 10 (Microsoft DaRT)

[ SOURCE ISO ]

* RS3.X64.EN-US

[ INSTALLATION & INFORMATION ]

* Create bootable USB (highly recommended) with Rufus,
* (attached) or burn to DVD-DL at slow speed.

* Hope you will enjoy this release!

* Regards,
* Generation2 @ TPB & 1337X
